<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cmn-Hans">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="renderer" content="webkit" />
    <meta name="full-screen" content="yes" />
    <meta name="x5-fullscreen" content="true" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="玩转打卡任务" />
    <meta name="description" content="玩转打卡任务" />
    <meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-siteapp" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no" />
    <meta name="msapplication-tap-highlight" content="no" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no,minimal-ui"
    />
    <title>玩转打卡任务</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="data:;base64,=" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/main.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="c-Header ">
      <img class="c-Img" src="./imgs/header@2x.png" alt="" />
    </div>

    <div class="c-Main u-NegativeMargin10">
      <div class="c-Panel">
        <div class="c-Panel-hd">
          <h3 class="c-Title">任意挑选手边教辅试卷，一分钟快速布置</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="c-Panel-bd">
          <div class="c-PanelItem">
            <div class="c-PanelItem-bd">
              <img class="c-Img" src="./imgs/img1@2x.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="c-PanelItem-ft u-NegativeMargin20">
              <p class="c-Text">
                设置好任务名称，可以附加上相应的文字或者图片进行补充。如需上传Word、PDF、PPT、Excel等格式，请前往智学网页版操作。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="c-Panel">
        <div class="c-Panel-hd">
          <h3 class="c-Title">
            老师添加答案，学生拍照打卡后查看答案。 轻松实现答案发布、自批自改。
          </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="c-Panel-bd">
          <div class="c-PanelItem">
            <div class="c-PanelItem-bd">
              <img class="c-Img" src="./imgs/img2@2x.png" alt="" />
              <img
                class="c-Img u-NegativeMargin40"
                src="./imgs/img2-2@2x.png"
                alt=""
              />
            </div>
            <div class="c-PanelItem-ft u-NegativeMargin20">
              <p class="c-Text">
                老师可以上传答案图片，并在发布时设置答案公布时间。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="c-PanelItem">
            <div class="c-PanelItem-bd">
              <img class="c-Img" src="./imgs/img2-3@2x.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="c-PanelItem-ft u-NegativeMargin20">
              <p class="c-Text">
                学生可以在提交任务并完成打卡后，或者任务截止时间后查看到相应答案.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="c-Panel">
        <div class="c-Panel-hd">
          <h3 class="c-Title">
            一键设置错题收集，学生错哪里、怎么错， 一目了然。
          </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="c-Panel-bd">
          <div class="c-PanelItem">
            <div class="c-PanelItem-bd">
              <img class="c-Img" src="./imgs/img3@2x.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="c-PanelItem-ft u-NegativeMargin20">
              <p class="c-Text">
                老师在发布任务时可以开启错题统计并设置题目总数。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="c-PanelItem">
            <div class="c-PanelItem-bd">
              <img class="c-Img" src="./imgs/img3-2@2x.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="c-PanelItem-ft u-NegativeMargin20">
              <p class="c-Text">
                学生可以在自己的任务报告中标记错题并上传作答或订正记录
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="c-PanelItem">
            <div class="c-PanelItem-bd">
              <img class="c-Img" src="./imgs/img3-3@2x.png" alt="" />
              <img
                class="c-Img u-NegativeMargin40"
                src="./imgs/img3-4@2x.png"
                alt=""
              />
            </div>
            <div class="c-PanelItem-ft u-NegativeMargin20">
              <p class="c-Text">
                老师可以在任务报告中查看学生的作答和标记错题
                情况，有针对性地对学生错题进行讲解。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="./js/flexible-custom.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
